[
  {
    "start": 14.521,
    "end": 18.67,
    "text": "The kettle wakes the kitchen with a hiss,"
  },
  {
    "start": 18.67,
    "end": 20.265,
    "text": "Then there is this,"
  },
  {
    "start": 20.265,
    "end": 21.861,
    "text": "upon my cheek -"
  },
  {
    "start": 21.861,
    "end": 24.335,
    "text": "a soft little kiss."
  },
  {
    "start": 24.335,
    "end": 26.888,
    "text": "The ordinary weight -"
  },
  {
    "start": 26.888,
    "end": 28.403,
    "text": "of a cup of tea."
  },
  {
    "start": 28.403,
    "end": 30.878,
    "text": "This stuff right here,"
  },
  {
    "start": 30.878,
    "end": 33.959,
    "text": "just you and me."
  },
  {
    "start": 34.308,
    "end": 39.176,
    "text": "Rain on the rooftop of the world,"
  },
  {
    "start": 39.176,
    "end": 43.164,
    "text": "Tiny tangled oaken brown curled."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.164,
    "end": 46.197,
    "text": "I've come back into something,"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.197,
    "end": 47.472,
    "text": "the scene of this."
  },
  {
    "start": 47.472,
    "end": 54.095,
    "text": "Right in the moments that I miss."
  },
  {
    "start": 54.095,
    "end": 58.963,
    "text": "Am I to know this right, was wrong?"
  },
  {
    "start": 58.963,
    "end": 64.069,
    "text": "Am I the one who really wrote this song?"
  },
  {
    "start": 64.069,
    "end": 67.739,
    "text": "Secrets written between the lines,"
  },
  {
    "start": 67.739,
    "end": 72.846,
    "text": "Find them one by one,"
  },
  {
    "start": 72.846,
    "end": 81.911,
    "text": "yours and mine."
  },
  {
    "start": 82.26,
    "end": 87.367,
    "text": "Tiny feed across the matted floor,"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.367,
    "end": 91.834,
    "text": "A little figure standing by the door."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.834,
    "end": 94.308,
    "text": "Sweet daffodil of mine,"
  },
  {
    "start": 94.308,
    "end": 101.06,
    "text": "Was this all by design?"
  },
  {
    "start": 101.409,
    "end": 104.043,
    "text": "Something in the chest still hums a note,"
  },
  {
    "start": 104.043,
    "end": 110.584,
    "text": "An old and half-remembered antidote —"
  },
  {
    "start": 110.584,
    "end": 113.617,
    "text": "It calls me to the high, the thin, the free,"
  },
  {
    "start": 113.617,
    "end": 121.724,
    "text": "Our hearth was lit by you, by me."
  },
  {
    "start": 122.073,
    "end": 127.34,
    "text": "Rain on the rooftop of the world,"
  },
  {
    "start": 127.34,
    "end": 132.206,
    "text": "Little strands round my fingers curled."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.206,
    "end": 136.037,
    "text": "The very scent, can I now recall,"
  },
  {
    "start": 136.037,
    "end": 137.473,
    "text": "Swear, I'd give anything,"
  },
  {
    "start": 137.473,
    "end": 142.181,
    "text": "anything at all."
  },
  {
    "start": 142.181,
    "end": 147.366,
    "text": "Am I to know that I belong?"
  },
  {
    "start": 147.366,
    "end": 152.074,
    "text": "How do we judge this right or wrong?"
  },
  {
    "start": 152.074,
    "end": 156.144,
    "text": "Secrets are written between the lines,"
  },
  {
    "start": 156.144,
    "end": 161.856,
    "text": "Find them one by one, yours and mine."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.206,
    "end": 170.105,
    "text": "The kettle goes quiet,"
  },
  {
    "start": 170.105,
    "end": 172.659,
    "text": "A little riot, a roar,"
  },
  {
    "start": 172.659,
    "end": 177.686,
    "text": "Miss those days that came before,"
  },
  {
    "start": 177.686,
    "end": 180.479,
    "text": "But most of all,"
  },
  {
    "start": 180.479,
    "end": 183.111,
    "text": "of that I miss."
  },
  {
    "start": 183.111,
    "end": 188.138,
    "text": "upon my cheek"
  },
  {
    "start": 188.138,
    "end": 191.967,
    "text": "that little kiss,"
  }
]
